{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhy1ma1ekn40","created":1776694448931,"text":"JVM","note":"源代码文件 -> 字节码文件(编译器) -> 机器码文件(JVM)；\n.java文件，启用javac编译器进程，编译成.class文件；然后，操作系统启用JVM进程，初始化运行环境，包括类加载器、内存空间、垃圾回收线程；\n1.类加载器\n2.运行时数据区\n3.执行引擎："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhyoy1vwbaw0","created":1776760257082,"text":"内存模型","layout_right_offset":{"x":-61,"y":-1}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhyoy5dqvq80","created":1776760264691,"text":"堆"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhyp2dsxvbs0","created":1776760596481,"text":"存放new出来的对象"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhyoyb4i3a80","created":1776760277193,"text":"虚拟机栈"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhyp67vmkug0","created":1776760897039,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhyoyh8bgzk0","created":1776760290484,"text":"本地方法栈"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhyp2xjjfag0","created":1776760639448,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhyoyvw9zk80","created":1776760322408,"text":"程序计数器"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhyp2qcij3k0","created":1776760623786,"text":"当前线程执行的字节码行号指示器"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhyoz0ym2sg0","created":1776760333433,"text":"方法区"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}